  "detailed_description": "Half Human, Half Hungry<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRaider of the lost Nosh!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPrehistorik, a member of the T-Bone Tribe, is hungry and ready for a bronco lunch! Armed with Diner-Club, his faithful frazzler, he sets off on his food-spotting expedition. Follow Prehistorik from the unexplored ice-fields of Antarctica, the darkened mysterious caverns of the shady continent to the lush jungles of the Tropics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeaturing<br />\r\n- Rhino Dendron<br />\r\n- King-Kongorus XII<br />\r\n- Chimp-Agogo<br />\r\n- Boa-Dee-Sauce<br />\r\n- Pyro-Tax<br />\r\n- And many other Chops<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLunch is served!",
